description: Warming and hearty, this vegetable soup has subtle umami flavours. Add a protein if you prefer, such as shredded chicken or a boiled egg.
keywords: Vegetable soup,Pescatarian,Low saturated fat,Tree nut free,Egg free,Jun 2020,Winter,Low sugar,Sesame free,Mushroom,May 2020,Halal,Low kilojoule,Soy free,Vegetarian,Vegan,Low fat,Spinach,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Vegetable Soup Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat. Add onion, carrot, celery and garlic and cook, stirring, for 5 minutes. Add stock and sauces and bring to the boil. Reduce heat to low and simmer for 15 minutes or until vegetables have softened.
Add mushroom and spinach and cook for 2 minutes or until softened. Ladle soup into bowls. Serve.
